{"tid":553301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★公屋男想靠「炒股」上車 月入1.7萬元，有流動資金約30萬元。","createTime":"2018-02-07T10:14:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-07T13:02:50.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3ac812155255003e49e521f323cf26d10c4b8366","tid":553301,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T10:14:33.000Z","msg":"個案主角：黃先生（24歲未婚，住公屋），月入1.7萬元，有流動資金約30萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">每年有最少12%增薪率</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n理財目標：他希望在大約30歲時，能在市區買到約400平方呎的物業自住，地區暫定為港鐵荃灣綫沿線15 分鐘步程之內。他希望利用股票作資產增值。<br />\n<br />\n用以下方向投資增值：<br />\n<br />\n（1）撥24萬元手頭現金作分段投入；每月再投入盈餘中的4,000 元（餘下4,000 元暫放在活期戶口）；<br />\n<br />\n（2）投資工具<span style=\"color: red;\">選用收息港股</span>及亞洲股票基金，<span style=\"color: red;\">假設每年平均9%回報</span>，6年後投資資產部分料可滾存至約80萬元，連同放在活期戶口那每月4,000元盈餘，總資產約可累積至110萬元；黃先生在中段時間也可將放在活期戶口的部分盈餘投入作投資。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E3%80%90%E7%90%86%E8%B2%A1%E5%80%8B%E6%A1%88%E3%80%91%E5%85%AC%E5%B1%8B%E7%94%B7%E6%83%B3%E9%9D%A0%E3%80%8C%E8%82%A1%E3%80%8D%E4%B8%8A%E8%BB%8A%EF%BC%88%E9%84%BA%E7%BF%A0%E7%8E%B2%EF%BC%89-041153522.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E7%2590%2586%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%25A1%2588%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25B1%258B%25E7%2594%25B7%25E6%2583%25B3%25E9%259D%25A0%25E3%2580%258C%25E8%2582%25A1%25E3%2580%258D%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25BB%258A%25EF%25BC%2588%25E9%2584%25BA%25E7%25BF%25A0%25E7%258E%25B2%25EF%25BC%2589-041153522.html&d=0NtIp6AWbsTciRjD%2FUosWARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=566be608\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E3%80%90%E7%90%86%E8%B2%A1%E5%80%8B%E6%A1%88%E3%80%91%E5%85%AC%E5%B1%8B%E7%94%B7%E6%83%B3%E9%9D%A0%E3%80%8C%E8%82%A1%E3%80%8D%E4%B8%8A%E8%BB%8A%EF%BC%88%E9%84%BA%E7%BF%A0%E7%8E%B2%EF%BC%89-041153522.html</a>